  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK933">
<l>uruḷāya mōvātu kūṟiṟ poruḷāyam</l>
<l>pōoyp puṟamē paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the king is incessantly addicted to the rolling dice in the hope of gain, his wealth and the resources thereof will take their departure and fall into other's hands.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
